      </h2>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='declarative'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '陳述句 chénshùjù', 'a declarative sentence')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述句</a>
        Declarative Sentences
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '陳述句 chénshùjù', 'a declarative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=13534' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '敘述 xùshù', 'to narrate / to recount')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">叙述</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2274' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiàn', 'a document')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">件</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1219' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'matter / thing / item')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">事</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1514' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '說明 shuōmíng', 'to explain')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">说明</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10039' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '觀點 guāndiǎn', 'point of view / viewpoint')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">观点</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=16963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '陳述句 chénshùjù', 'a declarative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5549' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mò', 'end / final stage / latter part')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">末</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2770' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '句號 jùhào', 'period / full stop')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句号</a>“。”。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        Declarative sentences narrate an event or describe a point of view.
        They end in a period.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=2503' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'Dìqiú', 'Earth')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">地球</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=654' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hěn', 'very')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">很</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1114' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dà', 'big / huge / large / major')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">大</a>。 (The Earth is big.)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=521' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '他們 tāmen', 'they')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">他们</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2147' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '題 tí', 'topic / subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">题</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4136' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zúqiú', 'football / soccer')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">足球</a>。 (They are playing soccer.)
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='interrogative'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a>
        Interrogative Sentences
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2147' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '題 tí', 'topic / subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">题</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=275' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chū', 'to go out')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">出</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=702' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '問題 wèntí', 'problem / question')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">问题</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5549' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mò', 'end / final stage / latter part')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">末</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2774' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '問號 wènhào', 'question mark')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">问号</a>“？”。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        Interrogative sentences raise a question and end in a question mark.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=3794' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '誰 shéi', 'who')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谁</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10953' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qiāo', 'to extort / to knock / to strike')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">敲</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2137' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '門 mén', 'opening / door / gate / doorway / gateway')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">门</a>？ (Who is knocking on the door?)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=350' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '幾 jǐ', 'several')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">几</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=814' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '歲 suì', 'years old')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">岁</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>？ (How old are you?)
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4792' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chī', 'to eat')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吃</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4784' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '飽 bǎo', 'to eat till full / to be satisfied')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">饱</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>？ (Are you full?)
        </li>
      </ol>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=398' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yǒu', 'is / are / to have')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">有</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=307' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qī', 'seven')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">七</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1590' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '種 zhǒng', 'kind / type / race / breed / seed / species')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">种</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        There are seven types of interrogative sentence:
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '語氣助詞 yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a>
          (Questions that use the modal particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>吗</a>) 
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '陳述句 chénshùjù', 'a declarative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3230' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wěi', 'tail')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">尾</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=367' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiā', 'add')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">加</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '語氣助詞 yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>”，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=16963' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '陳述句 chénshùjù', 'a declarative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">陈述句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9269' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '詞序 cíxù', 'word order')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词序</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=502' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bù', 'not / no')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2727' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '變 biàn', 'to become / to change')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">变</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
            (Add the modal particle <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>吗</a> to the end of a declarative sentence.  The word order of the declarative sentence
            does not change.
            For example)
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4792' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chī', 'to eat')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吃</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4352' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '飯 fàn', 'food / cuisine / cooked rice / meal')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">饭</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>？ (Are you going to eat?)
              <p/>
            </li>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3548' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huí', 'to go back / to turn around / to answer / to return / to revolve')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">回</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=117' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '美國 Měiguó', 'United States')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">美国</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1823' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '嗎 ma', 'indicates a question')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吗</a>？ (Are you American?)
              <p/>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問代詞 yíwèn dàicí', 'interrogative pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问代词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a>
          (Questions that use interrogative pronouns)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問代詞 yíwèn dàicí', 'interrogative pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问代词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=599' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kěyǐ', 'can / may / possible / able to')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">可以</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fàng', 'to put / to place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">放</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9260' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '賓語 bīnyǔ', 'object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宾语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2758' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèizhi', 'position / place / seat')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">位置</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
            (The interrogative pronoun can be placed in the location of the subject, the object, or the predicate.
            For example,)
          <p>
          <ol>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=3794' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '誰 shéi', 'who')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谁</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=15081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiābān', 'to work overtime')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">加班</a>？
              (Who is doing overtime?)<p/>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問代詞 yíwèn dàicí', 'interrogative pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问代词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=3794' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '誰 shéi', 'who')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谁</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fàng', 'to put / to place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">放</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2758' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèizhi', 'position / place / seat')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">位置</a>。
              (The interrogative pronoun <a href='/word_detail.php?id=3794' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '誰 shéi', 'who')" 
              onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>谁</a>
              is placed at the position of the subject.)
            </li>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qù', 'to go')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">去</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10355' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '哪裡 nǎlǐ', 'which / who / what')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哪里</a>？
              (Where are you going?)<p/>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問代詞 yíwèn dàicí', 'interrogative pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问代词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10355' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '哪裡 nǎlǐ', 'which / who / what')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">哪里</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fàng', 'to put / to place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">放</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9260' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '賓語 bīnyǔ', 'object')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">宾语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2758' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèizhi', 'position / place / seat')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">位置</a>。
              (The interrogative pronoun <a href='/word_detail.php?id=10355' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '哪裡 nǎlǐ', 'which / who / what')" 
              onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>哪里</a> is placed in the position of the object.)
            </li>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3966' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '車 chē', 'vehicle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">车</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2658' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '怎麼 zěnme', 'how')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">怎么</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>？ (What is wrong with your car?)<p/>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=9305' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問代詞 yíwèn dàicí', 'interrogative pronoun')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问代词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2658' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '怎麼 zěnme', 'how')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">怎么</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'fàng', 'to put / to place')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">放</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=328' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zài', 'in / at')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">在</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2758' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wèizhi', 'position / place / seat')" 
