              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=16973' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '偏正詞組 piān zhèng cízǔ', 'an endocentric phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">偏正词组</a> ＋ <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">呢</a>
              (endocentric phrase + <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'ne', 'question particle for subjects already mentioned')" 
              onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>呢</a>)
            </li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a>
          Questions using <a href='/word_detail.php?id=402' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'more')" 
          onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>多</a>
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '這 zhè', 'this / these')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">这</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1590' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '種 zhǒng', 'kind / type / race / breed / seed / species')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">种</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20462' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '疑問句 yíwèn jù', 'an interrogative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">疑问句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '副詞 fùcí', 'adverb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">副词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=13549' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '詢問 xúnwèn', 'to inquire')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">询问</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1368' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chéngdù', 'degree (level or extent) / level')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">程度</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=857' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '數量 shùliàng', 'quantity')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">数量</a>？“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9338' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '後面 hòumian', 'rear / back / behind / later / afterwards')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">后面</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16775' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhǐnéng', 'can only / obliged to do something')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">只能</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=776' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '帶 dài', 'to wear / to carry / to lead / to bring')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">带</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=301' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yī', 'one')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=281' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '個 gè', 'individual / unit')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">个</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=5495' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '詞 cí', 'word / works / phrases / classical Chinese poem / diction')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">词</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1783' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yībān', 'same / ordinary / common / general')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">一般</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=277' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shì', 'is / are / am / yes / to be')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">是</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9492' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '單音 dānyīn', 'monosyllabic')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">单音</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9290' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '形容詞 xíngróngcí', 'adjective')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">形容词</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
            (This kind of sentence uses the adverb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=402' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'more')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>多</a> to ask about degree or quantity.
            There can only be a single word after <a href='/word_detail.php?id=402' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'more')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>多</a>, which is usually a monosyllabic adjective.
            For example,)
          </p>
          <ol>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=754' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nà', 'that')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">那</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9645' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kē', 'measure word for for trees, cabbages, plants, etc')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">棵</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2647' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '樹 shù', 'tree')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">树</a><span class='hl'>多</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=953' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gāo', 'high / tall')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">高</a>？
              (How tall is that tree?)
              <p/>
            </li>
            <li class='secondLevel'>
              <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4081' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'nǐ', 'you')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">你</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4014' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '母親 mǔqīn', 'mother')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">母亲</a><span class='hl'>多</span><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1114' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'dà', 'big / huge / large / major')" 
              onmouseout="hideToolTip()">大</a>？
              (How old is your mother?)
              <p/>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='imperative'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20463' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '祈使句 qíshǐ jù', 'an imperative sentence')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">祈使句</a>
        Imperative Sentences
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20463' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '祈使句 qíshǐ jù', 'an imperative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">祈使句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16964' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cuīcù', 'to urge')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">催促</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=560' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'mìnglìng', 'an order / a command')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">命令</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=4459' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '請求 qǐngqiú', 'to request')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">请求</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=13096' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '勸告 quàngào', 'to advise')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">劝告</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1216' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'děng', 'et cetera / and so on / degree')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">等</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=20648' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'qíshǐ', 'imperative')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">祈使</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9308' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '語氣 yǔqì', 'tone / manner of speaking / mood')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=11171' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '語調 yǔdiào', 'intonation')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语调</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3230' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wěi', 'tail')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">尾</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2770' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '句號 jùhào', 'period / full stop')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句号</a>“。”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2027' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'huò', 'or')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">或</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16942' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆號 gǎntànhào', 'an exclamation mark (!)')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹号</a>“！”。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=20463' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '祈使句 qíshǐ jù', 'an imperative sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">祈使句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1641' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '經常 jīngcháng', 'frequently / constantly / regularly / often')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">经常</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10184' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'búyòng', 'need not')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">不用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9249' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '主語 zhǔyǔ', 'subject')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">主语</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=9250' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '謂語 wèiyǔ', 'predicate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">谓语</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cháng', 'always / ever / often / frequently / common / general')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">常</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=951' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yóu', 'follow / from / it is for...to / reason / cause')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">由</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9255' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '充當 chōngdāng', 'to serve as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">充当</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        Imperative sentences express a command, a request, or advice in an imperative tone.
        A period or explamation mark is used at the end of the sentence.
        The subject is often missing and the predicate is usually a verb.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=1181' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'kuài', 'fast / quick')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">快</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1343' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zǒu', 'to walk / to go / to move / to leave')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">走</a>！
          (Quick, go!)
          <p/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4792' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chī', 'to eat')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">吃</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4352' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '飯 fàn', 'food / cuisine / cooked rice / meal')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">饭</a>！
          (Eat!)
          <p/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '請 qǐng', 'to ask / to invite / please')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">请</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1644' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '進 jìn', 'to advance / to enter')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">进</a>！
          (Come in!)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=2994' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'shǒu', 'head / chief / first')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">首</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=8423' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chángyòng', 'commonly used')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">常用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9256' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '動詞 dòngcí', 'verb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">动词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '請 qǐng', 'to ask / to invite / please')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">请</a>”。
            (The verb <a href='/word_detail.php?id=279' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '請 qǐng', 'to ask / to invite / please')" 
            onmouseout='hideToolTip()'>请</a> is often used at the beginning of the sentence.)
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h3 class='article'>
        <a name='exclamatory'></a>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20464' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆句 gǎntàn jù', 'an exclamatory sentence')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹句</a>
        Exclamatory Sentences
      </h3>
      <p>
        <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20464' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆句 gǎntàn jù', 'an exclamatory sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=334' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'biǎoshì', 'to express')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">表示</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=13569' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '厭惡 yànwù', 'to loath / to hate')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">厌恶</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=13720' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '讚美 zànměi', 'to admire / to applause / to praise / to eulogize')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">赞美</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=8894' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '喜愛 xǐ ài', 'to like / to love')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">喜爱</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=12663' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '驚訝 jīngyà', 'amazed / astonished / surprised / amazing')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">惊讶</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1216' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'děng', 'et cetera / and so on / degree')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">等</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1316' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, ' 各種 gèzhǒng', 'every kind of / all kinds / various kinds')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">各种</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=4245' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gǎnqíng', 'feeling / emotion / affection / sensation')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感情</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1632' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòu', 'again / also')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">又</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16941' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆 gǎntàn', 'to sigh')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=11171' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '語調 yǔdiào', 'intonation')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语调</a>。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=6711' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jù', 'sentence / clause / phrase')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3230' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'wěi', 'tail')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">尾</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=16942' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆號 gǎntànhào', 'an exclamation mark (!)')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹号</a>“！”。<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" 
        onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>：
      </p>
      <p>
        Exclamatory sentences express admiration, love, surprise, loathing and other emotions in an exclamatory tone.
        An exclamation mark is used at the end of the sentence.
        For example,
      </p>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=714' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jīntiān', 'today')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">今天</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3133' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '天氣 tiānqì', 'weather')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">天气</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3348' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhēn', 'real / true / genuine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">真</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3536' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'lěng', 'cold')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">冷</a>！
          (It is freezing today!)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20464' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆句 gǎntàn jù', 'an exclamatory sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1641' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '經常 jīngcháng', 'frequently / constantly / regularly / often')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">经常</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=721' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'yòng', 'to use')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">用</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=953' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'gāo', 'high / tall')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">高</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=1368' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'chéngdù', 'degree (level or extent) / level')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">程度</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=273' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'de', 'possessive particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">的</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9271' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '副詞 fùcí', 'adverb')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">副词</a>，<a href='/word_detail.php?id=2846' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'bǐrú', 'for example / for instance / such as')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">比如</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=3348' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhēn', 'real / true / genuine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">真</a>”、“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=539' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tài', 'very / extremely')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">太</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=1216' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'děng', 'et cetera / and so on / degree')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">等</a>。
            (Exclamatory sentences often use adverbs expressing a high degree, such as <a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a>、<a href='/word_detail.php?id=3348' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'zhēn', 'real / true / genuine')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">真</a>、and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=539' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'tài', 'very / extremely')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">太</a>.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href='/word_detail.php?id=4031' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'háizǐ', 'child')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">孩子</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=400' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'duō', 'indicates a number greater than the number preceding it')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">多</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9478' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '聰明 cōngming', 'clever / intelligent / bright / smart / acute')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">聪明</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" 
          onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a>！
          (That child is so beautiful!)
          <p>
            <a href='/word_detail.php?id=20464' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '感嘆句 gǎntàn jù', 'an exclamatory sentence')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">感叹句</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=3858' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'cháng', 'always / ever / often / frequently / common / general')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">常</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=367' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'jiā', 'add')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">加</a><a href='/word_detail.php?id=9309' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, '語氣助詞 yǔqì zhùcí', 'modal particle')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">语气助词</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a>”<a href='/word_detail.php?id=387' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'hé', 'and')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">和</a>“<a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a>”。
            (The modal particles <a href='/word_detail.php?id=10174' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'a', 'expressing affirmation, approval, or consent')" onmouseout="hideToolTip()">啊</a> and <a href='/word_detail.php?id=393' onmouseover="showToolTip(this, 'le', 'completion of an action')" 
            onmouseout="hideToolTip()">了</a> are often added to exclamatory sentences.)
          </p>
        </li>
      </ol>
